		<technology>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The described process involves the chemical treatment of aluminum (Al), silver (Ag), and silicon (Si) for recycling purposes. The aluminum undergoes remelting and chemical treatment to enable its use as a substitute for virgin materials during the module assembling process in photovoltaic (PV) production. Similarly, chemical treatment is essential for the recycling of silicon in polysilicon production and for silver in the manufacturing of multi-Si PV cells. This process is specifically geared towards PV industry applications, supplying recycled high-purity materials for use in solar module manufacturing.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">所描述的工艺涉及铝（Al）、银（Ag）和硅（Si）的化学处理，用于回收目的。铝需要进行重熔和化学处理以在光伏（PV）生产的组件组装过程中替代原始材料。同样，硅在多晶硅生产中的回收和银在多硅光伏电池制造中都需要进行化学处理。这一过程专门针对光伏行业应用，为太阳能组件制造提供回收的高纯度材料。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="96ebf9c9-18bd-6e9c-1b4a-db9447d9b728" uri="../sources/96ebf9c9-18bd-6e9c-1b4a-db9447d9b728.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">MGIfbDG72oXc3nx9Ul2c5BEPnAm.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
	</processInformation>
